{"url":"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/post-5031","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<title>ドライブ日和を満喫できました&#x1f697; | アルプ薬局 ブログ</title>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n\n<!-- All in One SEO Pack 2.3.12 by Michael Torbert of Semper Fi Web Design[40,82] -->\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/staff/post-5031\" />\n<!-- /all in one seo pack -->\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//ajax.googleapis.com' />\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//s.w.org' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='style-css'  href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/style.css?ver=4.7.3' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<script type='text/javascript' src='http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js?ver=4.7.3'></script>\n<link rel='shortlink' href='https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/?p=5031' />\n\n<link rel=\"pingback\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/xmlrpc.php\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosansjapanese.css\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/mplus1p.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/touch.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/tabmenu.js\"></script>\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon-precomposed\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/webclip.png\" />\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp.ico\">\n<!--[if lt IE 9]>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/respond.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/js/html5.js\"></script>\n<![endif]-->\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\t\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-Y3YBPRXKL3\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-Y3YBPRXKL3');\n</script>\n<div id=\"wrapper\">\n\n<header id=\"site-header\" role=\"banner\">\n\t\n\n<div class=\"site-title\"><h1><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp\" rel=\"home\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/logo.png\" width=\"180\"  alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></a></h1></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"blog-title\"><h2>スタッフブログ</h2></div>\n<div class=\"blog-title2\"><p>アルプスタッフがつぶやく、日々の徒然日記</p></div><div class=\"blog-title-img\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-blog-01.jpg\"></div>\n\n\n\n\n</header>\n\n<div id=\"content\">   \n\n\t<div class=\"post\"> \n<div class=\"post-single\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<div id=\"breadcrumb\">\n        <span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"><a href=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">TOP</span> </a></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"bread\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb\"> <a href=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/category/staff\" itemprop=\"url\"><span itemprop=\"title\">スタッフブログ</span></a></span>\t\t</div>\n\n\n<article itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\" role=\"main\">\n\n<header>\n<h1 itemprop=\"headline\">ドライブ日和を満喫できました&#x1f697;</h1>\n<div class=\"align-right\"><p><i class=\"fa fa-calendar\"></i> <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2026-03-05T00:00:17+00:00\">2026/03/05</time></p></div>\n</header>\n\n\n<div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n<p>久しぶりの<span style=\"color: #ff6600\"><strong>良い天気☀️</strong></span>の<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">日曜日</span></strong>という事で、</p>\n<p>家族で<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">七尾市</span></strong>まで<strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">ドライブ&#x1f697;</span></strong>に行ってきました！</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">子供達</span></strong>は、車に乗るなり、嬉しくて、<strong><span style=\"color: #ff00ff\">「しゅぱーつ」&#x1f697;&#x1f64c;</span></strong>と腕を上げて</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">叫んでおりました。</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><strong>能越自動車道</strong></span>で<strong>約1時間&#x1f697;&#x1f4a8;</p>\n<p></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">綺麗な海</span></strong>&#x1f30a;&#x1f30a;が見えて<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">大興奮</span></strong>！！&#x1f38a;&#x1f44f;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"color: #008000\"><strong>道の駅 能登食祭市場<span style=\"color: #000000\">(七尾フィッシャーマンズワーフ)</span></strong></span>は</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5037\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1371-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1371-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1371-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1371-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1371.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff00ff\"><strong>ひな祭り</strong></span>が近いという事もあり、</p>\n<p>たくさんの<strong>お雛様&#x1f38e;</strong>が飾られており、子供達も<span style=\"color: #ff6600\"><b>びっくり</b></span>してました&#x1f632;❣️</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5036\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1375-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1375-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1375-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1375.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" />　　<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5039\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1383-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1383-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1383-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1383.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>また<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">能登ミルク</span></strong>を使用した、<strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">ソフトクリーム&#x1f366;</span></strong>を<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">「美味しい&#x1f606;」</span></strong>と言いながら、</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">食べてました&#x1f60b;</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5038\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1381-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1381-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1381-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1381-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1381.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">私は以前から食べたかった<strong><span style=\"color: #808080\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">蒸し牡蠣</span></span></strong>を食べれて<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">大満足</span></strong>でした&#x1f44f;&#x1f60b;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>雪もなく、久しぶりに<strong><span style=\"color: #008000\">公園</span></strong>で走り回ったり&#x1f3c3;&#x1f4a8;<strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">ブランコや滑り台</span></strong>を</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff00ff\"><strong>思いっきり楽しんだ&#x1f606;</strong></span>ようで</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5040\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1390-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1390-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1390-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/DSC_1390.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" />　　</span><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-5041\" src=\"http://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/1000002960-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/1000002960-225x300.jpg 225w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/1000002960-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/1000002960.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>帰りの道中</strong>は疲れ切って、子供たちは<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">すやすや寝て</span>&#x1f4a4;</strong>ました&#x1f604;</p>\n<p>久しぶりの<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\">良い天気☀️</span></strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\"><span style=\"color: #000000\">を</span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\">満喫</span></span></strong>出来た一日でした&#x1f44f;&#x1f601;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n調剤薬局部　Ｎ</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"blog-alp-logo\"><img src=\"https://www.alp-grp.jp/blog/wp-content/themes/alp-blog/img/alp-logo.jpg\" width=\"130\" alt=\"アルプ薬局\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ninja_onebutton\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n//<![CDATA[\n(function(d){\nif(typeof(window.NINJA_CO_JP_ONETAG_BUTTON_2e525997ea6182d4250a7da41cf17aa6)=='undefined'){\n    document.write(\"<sc\"+\"ript type='text\\/javascript' src='\\/\\/omt.shinobi.jp\\/b\\/2e525997ea6182d4250a7da41cf17aa6'><\\/sc\"+\"ript>\");\n}else{\n    window.NINJA_CO_JP_ONETAG_BUTTON_2e525997ea6182d4250a7da41cf17aa6.ONETAGButton_Load();}\n})(document